@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### 1. SKU名一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/sku-names
Accept: application/json

### 2. ユニークなSKUリスト取得 (決済データから)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sku-names/distinct-skus
Accept: application/json

### 3. 親SKU一覧取得
GET {{baseUrl}}/sku-names/parent-skus
Accept: application/json

### 4. SKU名の保存
POST {{baseUrl}}/sku-names
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "TEST-SKU-001",
  "japaneseName": "テスト商品001",
  "parentSku": "PARENT-SKU-001"
}

### 5. 親SKUの作成
POST {{baseUrl}}/sku-names/parent-sku
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "japaneseName": "新規テスト親商品"
}
